                "list": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "List",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p><strong>304 Stainless Steel</strong> — Medical-grade, corrosion-resistant, and fully recyclable at end of life. It's the same alloy used in surgical instruments, chosen because it won't leach, corrode, or degrade in contact with water.</p><p><strong>Borosilicate Glass</strong> — Chemically inert and heat-resistant, used anywhere the water itself is visible or held. It never absorbs odor or flavor from what passes through it.</p><p><strong>Brushed Metal Hardware</strong> — Every fitting and connector is solid metal, not plated plastic, so the parts that see the most wear are also the most durable.</p><p><strong>FSC-Certified Packaging</strong> — Every box is sourced from responsibly managed forests and is fully recyclable — no plastic void-fill, no single-use foam.</p>",
